 {"question": "Is Navattic better than Storylane?", "answer": "Navattic produces higher-fidelity demos through HTML/CSS capture and offers stronger marketing analytics. Storylane is faster to create demos, more affordable ($40/month vs. $500/month), and more accessible to non-technical users. Choose Navattic for website-embedded demos where visual fidelity and marketing attribution matter. Choose Storylane for broader demo production across marketing, sales, and customer success where speed and volume are priorities."},
